<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Vitor Elian — Perfil</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&family=DM+Serif+Display&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --accent: #7F77DD;
      --accent-light: #EEEDFE;
      --bg: #F4F3F0;
      --surface: #FFFFFF;
      --border: rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
      --text: #1a1a1a;
      --muted: #888780;
      --radius: 16px;
      --sidebar-w: 210px;
    }

    html, body {
      min-height: 100vh;
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
    }

    body {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: var(--sidebar-w) 1fr;
      grid-template-rows: 1fr auto;
      grid-template-areas:
        "sidebar main"
        "footer  footer";
      gap: 12px;
      padding: 12px;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    /* SIDEBAR */
    .sidebar {
      grid-area: sidebar;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .avatar-wrap {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
    }

    .avatar {
      width: 120px;
      height: 120px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      border: 3px solid var(--surface);
      background: var(--accent-light);
      overflow: hidden;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
      font-size: 38px;
      color: var(--accent);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(127,119,221,0.18);
    }

    .avatar img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
    }

    .sidebar-card {
      background: var(--surface);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      border: 0.5px solid var(--border);
      padding: 68px 18px 20px;
      margin-top: -52px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      flex: 1;
    }

    .sidebar-card h2 {
      font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
      font-size: 17px;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--text);
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 4px;
    }

    .sidebar-card .handle {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-top: 2px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .bio {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.6;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .divider {
      width: 100%;
      height: 0.5px;
      background: var(--border);
      margin: 8px 0 14px;
    }

    .social-list {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 4px;
      width: 100%;
      margin-top: auto;
    }

    .social-link {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--muted);
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 7px 10px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      transition: background 0.15s, color 0.15s;
    }

    .social-link:hover {
      background: var(--accent-light);
      color: var(--accent);
    }

    .social-link img {
      width: 22px;
      height: 22px;
      object-fit: contain;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    /* MAIN */
    .main-col {
      grid-area: main;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .card {
      background: var(--surface);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      border: 0.5px solid var(--border);
      padding: 24px 28px;
    }

    .article-card h1 {
      font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
      font-size: 36px;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--text);
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }

    .article-card p {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.75;
    }

    .gallery-card { flex: 1; }

    .gallery-header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    .gallery-header h2 {
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .gallery-count {
      font-size: 11px;
      color: var(--accent);
      background: var(--accent-light);
      padding: 2px 10px;
      border-radius: 20px;
    }

    .gallery-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr);
      grid-template-rows: 100px 100px;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .gallery-grid img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      border-radius: 10px;
      display: block;
      transition: transform 0.2s, opacity 0.2s;
    }

    .gallery-grid img:hover {
      transform: scale(1.03);
      opacity: 0.88;
    }

    .gallery-grid img:nth-child(1) {
      grid-column: 1 / 3;
      grid-row: 1 / 3;
    }

    .gallery-grid img:nth-child(4) {
      grid-column: 4 / 6;
      grid-row: 1 / 3;
    }

    /* FOOTER */
    footer {
      grid-area: footer;
      background: var(--surface);
      border-radius: 10px;
      border: 0.5px solid var(--border);
      padding: 12px 20px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 11px;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    /* ANIMATIONS */
    @keyframes fadeUp {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(14px); }
      to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }

    .sidebar      { animation: fadeUp 0.5s ease both 0.05s; }
    .article-card { animation: fadeUp 0.5s ease both 0.15s; }
    .gallery-card { animation: fadeUp 0.5s ease both 0.25s; }
    footer        { animation: fadeUp 0.5s ease both 0.3s;  }

    /* RESPONSIVE */
    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      body {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        grid-template-areas: "sidebar" "main" "footer";
      }
      .gallery-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
        grid-template-rows: auto;
        grid-auto-rows: 90px;
      }
      .gallery-grid img:nth-child(1),
      .gallery-grid img:nth-child(4) {
        grid-column: auto;
        grid-row: auto;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <aside class="sidebar">
    <div class="avatar-wrap">
      <div class="avatar">
        <img src="Imagens/imagem minion.png" alt="Foto de Vitor Elian"
             onerror="this.style.display='none'">
        VE
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="sidebar-card">
      <h2>Vitor Elian</h2>
      <span class="handle">@vitorelian</span>
      <p class="bio">Muita resenha por aqui!</p>
      <div class="divider"></div>
      <nav class="social-list">
        <a class="social-link" href="https://www.facebook.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          <img src="Imagens/facebook.png" alt="Logo Facebook"> Facebook
        </a>
        <a class="social-link" href="https://www.twitter.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          <img src="Imagens/twitter.png" alt="Logo Twitter"> Twitter
        </a>
        <a class="social-link" href="https://www.instagram.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          <img src="Imagens/instagram.png" alt="Logo Instagram"> Instagram
        </a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </aside>

  <div class="main-col">
    <div class="card article-card">
      <h1>Article title</h1>
      <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Donec vel sapien eget
        nunc efficitur commodo. Sed ut perspiciatis unde omnis iste natus error sit
        voluptatem accusantium doloremque laudantium.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card gallery-card">
      <div class="gallery-header">
        <h2>Galeria</h2>
        <span class="gallery-count">10 fotos</span>
      </div>
      <div class="gallery-grid">
        <img src="https://picsum.photos/500/400?1" alt="Foto 1">
        <img src="https://picsum.photos/400/500?2" alt="Foto 2">
        <img src="https://picsum.photos/300/360?3" alt="Foto 3">
        <img src="https://picsum.photos/200/400?4" alt="Foto 4">
        <img src="https://picsum.photos/400/600?5" alt="Foto 5">
        <img src="https://picsum.photos/600/450?6" alt="Foto 6">
        <img src="https://picsum.photos/200/200?7" alt="Foto 7">
        <img src="https://picsum.photos/490/500?8" alt="Foto 8">
        <img src="https://picsum.photos/200/200?9" alt="Foto 9">
        <img src="https://picsum.photos/200/200?10" alt="Foto 10">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <footer>
    <p>© 2024 Vitor Elian. All rights reserved.</p>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
